,"msg":"Show Blocked User - 浮浪人 屌你老母"},{"pid":"a70a7957fa3e18f07c34261fa6f53426acbcf747","tid":328163,"uid":36078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:47:04.000Z","msg":"咁唔like咪走囉，講到好似求係落香港咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266ba74f137498a4ec78536ca7934e57422448c4","tid":328163,"uid":36483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:48:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>( Show Blocked User - 浮浪人 )</blockquote>"},{"pid":"08295b9243b5cfaace1af20b7232216c695e41d0","tid":328163,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:52:32.000Z","msg":"講真人類既本質就係咁<br />\n邊有咩美好世界"},{"pid":"2f52b67d85066232f4630e131dd94648d0f93f12","tid":328163,"uid":92743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:55:18.000Z","msg":"假膠黎"},{"pid":"8272a2222ab029b975c0bb5370e00c7b0bee2d06","tid":328163,"uid":39826,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:55:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.szhome.com/360-58611-detail-175764566.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.szhome.com%2F360-58611-detail-175764566.html&d=dmgh%2FiratAcdaLvEFPzc8BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=9d2caccf\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.szhome.com/360-58611-detail-175764566.html</a><br />\n原POST <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n应了那句没人教育出去自然有人教育的老话！还不平时惯着，出去还任性！公交车又不是自己家，自己看着自己孩子可爱，在别人眼里就是个噪音器。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大把中國人覺得個阿媽本身都有問題 覺得佢有所隱瞞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8fdb94705412f5b140f69406b12c5ead43882dc","tid":328163,"uid":39826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:56:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://m.szhome.com/360-58611-detail-175764566.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.szhome.com%2F360-58611-detail-175764566.html&d=dmgh%2FiratA